short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A extension to integration Clockify and Kanbanize.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Integrate Clockify with Kanbanize using this extension and track time from anywhere on the web and improve productivity! 


Features of the extension:
- Effortless Time Tracking.
- Play new tasks: Just fill the project and tag and the extension create all the structures on Clockify.
- Pause the task: Do you need a break? Use the pause button to don't need fill the inputs again!
- Stop the task from anywhere!
- On Pause/Stop feature the time is registered in Clockify app and Kanbanize card.
